title: How to Be a Healthy Person - New Season Coming Sep. 21
description: What does it mean to be a healthy person? This will be a season about depending on the Holy Spirit for life change. We're going to spend 12 weeks in our Bibles talking about what it really means to change from the inside out. 12 weeks, 24 episodes. Join us for teaching on Tuesdays and some incredible guest convos every Thursday.
